These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, december, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, tulip, azalea
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, purple, lilac, apricot
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
10. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who's birthday is in september##7
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
12. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | february    | march | december    | september   |
| Flower   | lily | tulip | daisy | azalea |
| Color           | purple       | lilac   | apricot  | turquise     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

