.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, begonia, lily
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, traveling, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, old-henry, game
 1. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
 4. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
 7. the person who growslily is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 8. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Flower          | marigold   | begonia       | lily    | rose      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Hobby   | video-games   | magic-tricks  | rock-climbing       | traveling |
| Cigar         | dunhill      | old-henry  | game | ritmeester |

