The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, tennis, climbing, baseball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bongani, cain, baccarat
 1. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the person who growsiris is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person who growsorchid##6
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person who's sport is climbing is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Flower           | orchid | daisy | bellflower | iris |
