.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, coral, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, skiing
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, pony, mouse
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
 4. the person who likes orange is the owner of the pony##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Color      | fuchsia | coral       | lavender         | orange       |
| Hobby         | cooking     | video-games    | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks |
| Sport           | skiing   | parkour | soccer | lacrosse     |
| Pet   | mouse      | guinea-pig          | chinchilla           | pony |

