10. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
11. the turkish is the journalist##1
12. the scientist is somewhere between the journalist and the person who's sport is tennis##7
13. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

