 8. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the japanese##3
10. the colonial house is the italian##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the art-deco house##2
12. the modern house is the old-henry-smoker##1

