There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, mexican, nigerian
 1. the fan of country is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 2. the fan of techno is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 4. the fan of soul is the mexican##1
 5. the colombian is not the fan of country##6
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
 9. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the german is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
12. the person who's sport is badminton is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the nigerian is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
14. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
