 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
12. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person who likes apricot##6
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person eating onion##6
15. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person who likes chestnut and the person eating grapes##7

