.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-17::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, rabbit, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, mystery, scientific
City: liverpool, rome, hamburg, san-francisco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, iced-tea, coffee
 1. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 7. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 8. the owner of the goat is not the person drinking milk##6
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Pet         | ferret      | fish   | goat   | rabbit       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| City   | liverpool  | rome | hamburg   | san-francisco     |
| Beverage         | milk   | coffee    | soy-milk   | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, bike, scooter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, lily, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, august, april
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person who growssunflower##7
 8. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is the person who growslily##1
12. the person who growslily is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | airplane   | scooter     | bike   | skateboard |
| Flower       | sunflower   | begonia | dahlia | lily    |
| Birthday      | august | april | july   | may  |
| Pet        | rabbit | cat     | hamster   | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, soy-milk, water
There 4 different types of food: potato, plum, nectarine, kiwi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, scientific, zombie, family
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, july, february, august
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating nectarine and the person watching comedy movies##2
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person watching zombie movies##6
 7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating potato##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person eating potato##6
 9. the person watching family movies is not the person eating kiwi##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
11. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person eating nectarine is not the person drinking fanta##6
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
14. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
15. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | 7up        | water          | soy-milk    |
| Food         | kiwi | plum    | nectarine          | potato |
| Movie-Genre           | comedy  | scientific   | zombie | family      |
| Birthday   | august       | october | february          | july        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, helicopter, taxi
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, hot-chocolate, sprite
There 4 different types of food: pear, papaya, carrot, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating carrot is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 6. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person driving the scooter##7
 7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the person eating pear is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport   | taxi      | helicopter     | jet-ski   | scooter    |
| Beverage     | sprite | hot-chocolate   | tea | juice |
| Food     | kale        | carrot     | pear  | papaya      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 